(619, 'Urinary frequency', '', 'Renal and urinary disorders', 'A disorder characterized by urination at short intervals.', 'Please rate the following on a scale from 1 to 5: Urinary frequency', '', 1, 1, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
