(667, 'Vaginal discharge', '', 'Reproductive system and breast disorders', 'A disorder characterized by vaginal secretions. Mucus produced by the cervical glands is discharged from the vagina naturally, especially during the childbearing years.', 'Please rate the following on a scale from 1 to 5: Vaginal discharge', '', 1, 1, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
