(713, 'Pleural effusion', '', 'Respiratory, thoracic and mediastinal disorders', 'A disorder characterized by an increase in amounts of fluid within the pleural cavity. Symptoms include shortness of breath, cough and marked chest discomfort.', 'Please rate the following on a scale from 1 to 5: Pleural effusion', '', 1, 1, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
